condition.narrative: Finance Agreement :Establishment of the Project Steering Committee | Description :The Recipient shall establish, within 2 months ofthe Effective Date, and thereafter maintain, throughout the period of implementation of the Project, the Project Steering Committeewith functions, composition, and resources acceptable to the Association, as set forth in the Project Implementation Manual (PIM),to provide policy guidance and support to the Project Management Unit (PMU) and carry out inter-ministerial/inter-agencycoordination to facilitate Project implementation. | Due Date :15-Jun-2018

Finance Agreement :Financial Management Specialist | Description :The Recipient shall, within 2 months after the Effective Date,and thereafter maintain throughout the implementation of the project a financial management specialist with qualifications andexperience acceptable to the Association. | Due Date :15-Jun-2018

Finance Agreement :Maintenance of Project Management Unit | Description :The Recipient shall maintain, throughout the period ofimplementation of the Project, a PMU, within the Ministry of Livestock Development (MoLD), headed by a Project Director supportedwith adequate professional and administrative staff in numbers and with qualification and experience and under terms of referencesatisfactory to the Association, and provided with resources and powers as shall be required for it. | Due Date :31-Jan-2018

Finance Agreement :Procurement Specialist | Description :The Recipient shall, within 2 months after the Effective Date, andthereafter maintain throughout the implementation of the project a procurement specialist with qualifications and experienceacceptable to the Association. | Due Date :15-Jun-2018

Finance Agreement :Project Implementation Manual | Description :The Recipient shall, within 1 month of the Effective Date, prepareand adopt the Project Implementation Manual (PIM) in a manner and substance satisfactory to the Association. | Due Date :16-May-2018

No withdrawal shall be made for Emergency Expenditures under Category (6) unless and until the Association is satisfied that all ofthe conditions listed in Section IV.2(b) of Schedule 2 to the Financing Agreement have been met in respect of the said expenditures.
